      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1770997481910,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "OPENCODE AGENT FRAMEWORK\nsandbox/opencode/ at /opt/opencode/ (in-container)\n\n▸ 8 agent definitions (agents/*.md)\n  Default, Architect, Code Review, Debug, Documentation, Refactor, Security, Testing\n\n▸ 22 skill directories (skills/*/)\n  Bash, Browser, Code Analysis, Commit, Database, Deploy, Docker, File Ops, Git, etc.\n\n▸ 8 tool files (tools/*.ts)\n  Bash execution, file operations, web browsing, vision, code analysis, git, etc.\n\n▸ Background services (s6-overlay)\n  OpenCode API, Web UI, Browser stream/viewer, LSS sync, Presentation viewer",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 272,
      "containerId": "opencode-box",
      "originalText": "OPENCODE AGENT FRAMEWORK\nsandbox/opencode/ at /opt/opencode/ (in-container)\n\n▸ 8 agent definitions (agents/*.md)\n  Default, Architect, Code Review, Debug, Documentation, Refactor, Security, Testing\n\n▸ 22 skill directories (skills/*/)\n  Bash, Browser, Code Analysis, Commit, Database, Deploy, Docker, File Ops, Git, etc.\n\n▸ 8 tool files (tools/*.ts)\n  Bash execution, file operations, web browsing, vision, code analysis, git, etc.\n\n▸ Background services (s6-overlay)\n  OpenCode API, Web UI, Browser stream/viewer, LSS sync, Presentation viewer",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
