      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "SUB-THREAD ISOLATION RULES:\n• Each sub-thread starts with ZERO context — no conversation history\n• Sub-threads DO NOT see MEMORY.md — only the main agent reads/writes it\n• Main agent passes context IN the prompt. Only results flow UP.\n• Sub-threads are disposable: spawn → work → return results → terminate",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "st_note",
      "originalText": "SUB-THREAD ISOLATION RULES:\n• Each sub-thread starts with ZERO context — no conversation history\n• Sub-threads DO NOT see MEMORY.md — only the main agent reads/writes it\n• Main agent passes context IN the prompt. Only results flow UP.\n• Sub-threads are disposable: spawn → work → return results → terminate",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
